## geopm/integration/apps/README

This directory contains scripts to encapsulate launching applications
and benchmarks.  There may be more than one script for an application
to support different workloads or scenarios.  For some applications,
there are dedicated subdirectories containing more information on how
to download and build the application, and sometimes GEOPM-related
patches to be applied on top of publically-available source code.


Examples:

- dgemm.py: Uses geopmbench to run DGEMM sized to use power close to TDP.

- minife.py: Run MiniFE with a problem size appropriate for the number
      of nodes given as input.  Scripts for building the benchmark can be
      found in the minife subdirectory.
